@startuml
title Sequence: Xem nhiệm vụ (Kanban)
actor "Nhân viên" as Emp
participant "Browser\n(tasks.html)" as UI
participant "JwtAuthentication\nFilter" as Filter
participant "TaskController" as Ctrl
participant "TaskServiceImpl" as Svc
participant "TaskRepository" as Repo
participant "TaskMapper" as Mapper
database "MySQL" as DB

Emp -> UI : Truy cập trang /tasks
UI -> Filter : GET /api/tasks/my/{empId}\n+ Header: Bearer JWT
activate Filter
Filter -> Filter : extractJwt() → validateToken()
Filter -> Filter : Set SecurityContext
Filter --> Ctrl : Authenticated request
deactivate Filter

activate Ctrl
Ctrl -> Svc : getMyTasks(empId)
activate Svc

Svc -> Repo : findByAssignedToId(empId)
Repo -> DB : SELECT * FROM tasks\nWHERE assigned_to = ?
DB --> Repo : List<Task>
Repo --> Svc : List<Task> entities

Svc -> Mapper : toDTO() cho từng Task
note right
  Mapper flatten:
  assignedBy.fullName → assignedByName
  assignedTo.fullName → assignedToName
  priority (Enum) → String
  deadline (DateTime) → String
end note
Mapper --> Svc : List<TaskDTO>

Svc --> Ctrl : List<TaskDTO>
deactivate Svc
Ctrl --> UI : JSON Response
deactivate Ctrl

UI -> UI : JavaScript phân loại\nvào 4 cột Kanban:\nPENDING | ACCEPTED | DONE | OVERDUE
UI --> Emp : Hiển thị bảng Kanban
@enduml
